    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Usage</strong> etched onto a creature or armor</p><hr /><p>This angular rune channels the fury of dragon kind. Whenever a creature Strikes the rune-bearer or Steals from them, draconic sanction fully focuses on them, causing them to become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Off-Guard} for 1 round.</p><p><strong>Invocation</strong> As a free action, the rune-bearer can Fly up to 60 feet toward a creature that has damaged them in the last minute. If they end this movement adjacent to the creature, the creature becomes off-guard until the end of the rune-bearer's next turn. If the rune-bearer doesn't have a fly Speed and ends its movement in the air, they safely float back to the ground at the end of their next turn.</p>"
